The original signed consent form will be placed in the patient
 chart and scanned into Epic. BioNet will verify consent in Epic.  PBS (Study team)
 Media: DMEM + antibiotics (Study team)
 Media tubes (x3 per collection) (Study team)
 10% Formalin (Bionet)
 FFPE cassette x 5 (Bionet)
 Specimen container (Bionet)
 OCT compound (Bionet)
 OCT mold x 4 (Bionet)
 OCT quick freeze box (Bionet)
 Liquid nitrogen vapor (Bionet)
 Cryovials x 3 (Bionet)
 Collection kit containing 10 ml EDTA blood tubes x 2 (Bionet)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4qlk4","text":"Procurement and Processing:
 Tissue:
 Limitation: procedures should be scheduled at East Bank hospital in order to accommodate short

","type":"ordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"88ea5","text":"Study team will provide preop staff with blood tube collection kits. 2 x 10 ml EDTA blood tubes will be in a bag labeled with BLS pager number for pick up contact.
","type":"ordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9q5i3","text":"Blood tubes will be held at room temperature until delivery to TTL or pick up by study team.
","type":"ordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"djobl","text":"BLS will pick up blood tubes and submit to TTL for processing. ","type":"ordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2jtig","text":"Specimen Release: BioNet will email the research team when specimens are ready for pick-up. Specimens can be picked-up at the BioNet office before 4:00PM. Signature confirmation of

","type":"ordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"88bpq","text":"BLS will email study team for pickup ASAP since immediate pickup of fresh samples is ideal. Study team will pick up samples after 2pm.
","type":"ordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4u1mb","text":"Study team will pick up fresh, OCT, and snap frozen samples the same day.
","type":"ordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6hmi8","text":"If BLS was unable to submit blood to TTL, study team will pick up blood the same day.
","type":"ordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ac305","text":"Study team will pick up FFPE blocks when they are ready (~1-2 weeks after procedure day).
","type":"ordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5c34v","text":"Follow-Up: If collection containers or media are stored with BioNet, the researcher will provide new ones for future collections when needed.
